                     <interp inst="t18240603-24-person275" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am son of Susanah Schneider, a <rs id="t18240603-24-viclabel135" type="occupation">furrier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-24-victim272 t18240603-24-viclabel135"></join>, who lives in Regent-street, and is a widow; the prisoner was our <rs id="t18240603-24-deflabel136" type="occupation">errand boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-24-defend271 t18240603-24-deflabel136"></join>; this muff and tippet are my mother's; we had not missed them; my brother's handwriting is on them.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 16.</p>
